	<KARMARITUAL>Windmasters Karma Rituals incorporate often dizzying displays of flight and speed; the Karma Rituals magic enables the adept to fly without test or cost for the duration. The air attack is accompanied by a gust of wind focused to a knife-like blade that strikes a distant target.</KARMARITUAL>
	<HALFMAGIC>The adept can also use their Half-Magic to find other Windmasters and know the history of Windmasters. Additionally, the adept  can use Half-Magic for knowledge of guerilla and ambush warfare, history of windling battles and tactics, and traditional windling equipment and fightingstyles.</HALFMAGIC>
